{
  "texts": [
    "Gradually, they focussed on explaining the search directions (science).",
    "Today, we ask machines to explain their decisions for humans to be able to trust their line of reasoning (ethics).",
    "As a consequence, we expect machines to exhibit humanlike intelligence.",
    "In hard science, we focus on trustworthiness, and we use explainability.",
    "In law, we focus on explainability and search for trustworthiness.Considering the importance of explainability, law applications have become an exciting playground for experimenting with explanations and machine intelligence."
  ]
}